[COLOR red][B]Version 2.1.37[/B][/COLOR]
- Included episodes when considering hide watched items for widgets.
- Added "Autoplay Cloud Result" to each account's settings. Enable this and any cloud result found after a prescrape will be automatically played.
- Added "Avoid Episode Spoilers in Custom Windows" to Settings->Content->General. This will hide plot and thumb spoilers from FenLightAM's custom windows.
- Added "Retry With IMDb Year Data When No Results" to Settings->Results->General.
- Other changes/fixes.


